\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {8}{\ignorespaces Mean fixed-time condition balanced accuracy under fixed and adaptive control for the same \(60/20\) benchmark scale. The strongest direct-condition models are robust across regimes, while the mechanistic baseline benefits much more strongly from the simpler fixed controller.}}{20}{figure.caption.12}\protected@file@percent }
